OL,3,CRoyal Ballet and Opera thanks Timothee
OL,4,CChalamet for boosting ticket sales
OL,6,FA disparaging remark about opera and
OL,7,Fballet by Hollywood actor Timothee
OL,8,FChalamet appears to have fuelled a
OL,9,Fboost in ticket sales in the UK.
OL,11,FThe Marty Supreme star, who was
OL,12,Fnominated for an Oscar, came under
OL,13,Ffire in March after saying he does not
OL,14,Fwant to work in opera or ballet as "no
OL,15,Fone cares" about them.
OL,17,FBut the comments don't seem to be a
OL,18,Fbig concern for Alex Beard, chief
OL,19,Fexecutive of the Royal Ballet and
OL,20,FOpera, who said the public's reaction
OL,21,Fhas been "fantastic".
OL,26,@kD@erroD@arr
