OL,3,CRoyal Ballet and Opera thanks Timothee
OL,4,CChalamet for boosting ticket sales
OL,6,FIn an interview with The Times,
OL,7,Fpublished on Tuesday, Beard said the
OL,8,Fcharity was careful not to appear
OL,9,F"hoity-toity" when issuing a public
OL,10,Fresponse to the French-American actor.
OL,12,F"We simply said 'Take a look at what
OL,13,Fwe're doing, mate' ` for instance, the
OL,14,Ffact that the largest portion of our
OL,15,Faudience by age is 20 to 30-year-olds.
OL,17,F"And you know what? Our post got 2.5
OL,18,Fmillion engagements and half a million
OL,19,Fshares, just on Instagram. And our
OL,20,Fticket sales got an immediate boost.
OL,21,FSo cheers, Timmy!"
OL,26,@kD@err}D@RO]
