OL,3,CRoyal Ballet and Opera thanks Timothee
OL,4,CChalamet for boosting ticket sales
OL,6,FChalamet drew sharp criticism from the
OL,7,Fperforming arts world following an
OL,8,Finterview for US outlet Variety about
OL,9,Fthe future of cinema.
OL,11,F"I don't want to be working in ballet
OL,12,For opera or, you know, things where
OL,13,Fit's like, 'hey, keep this thing
OL,14,Falive', even though no one cares about
OL,15,Fthis anymore," he told fellow actor
OL,16,FMatthew McConaughey.
OL,18,F"All respect to the ballet and opera
OL,19,Fpeople out there", he quickly added.
OL,20,F"I just lost 14 cents in viewership. I
OL,21,Fjust took shots for no reason."
OL,26,@kD@err
