OL,3,CRoyal Ballet and Opera thanks Timothee
OL,4,CChalamet for boosting ticket sales
OL,6,FResponding to the remarks on social
OL,7,Fmedia, the Royal Ballet and Opera
OL,8,Fsaid: "Every night at the Royal Opera
OL,9,FHouse, thousands of people gather for
OL,10,Fballet and opera.
OL,12,F"For the music. For the storytelling.
OL,13,FFor the sheer magic of live
OL,14,Fperformance," they wrote. "If you'd
OL,15,Flike to reconsider, @tchalamet, our
OL,16,Fdoors are open."
OL,18,FChalamet did not respond to the
OL,19,Fbacklash at the time.
